{"tid":836713,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"向隅客終圓置業夢 黃小姐夥弟弟500萬購LP6一房","createTime":"2018-09-26T00:25:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-26T00:25:10.000Z","uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"af75e6447537ce1750924d1b4aa92590f03a1041","tid":836713,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T00:25:10.000Z","msg":"南豐日出康城LP6今日發售707伙，黃小姐剛斥資500萬元購入一個1房單位。黃小姐指單位與90後的弟弟合資購買，鐘情項目的會所，以及鄰近鐵路。她現居於港島區，手上亦有物業，是次為第一次購入一手物業，早前兩次入票LP6但未有成功，亦有入票港島區新盤但同樣落空。黃太笑指，昨日是中秋節，大時大節便有置業的念頭。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static01.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2165000/2167958/photo6147825435015227447_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2165000%2F2167958%2Fphoto6147825435015227447_1024.jpg&h=4d22a94d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://ps.hket.com/article/2167958/%E5%90%91%E9%9A%85%E5%AE%A2%E7%B5%82%E5%9C%93%E7%BD%AE%E6%A5%AD%E5%A4%A2+%E9%BB%83%E5%B0%8F%E5%A7%90%E5%A4%A5%E5%BC%9F%E5%BC%9F500%E8%90%AC%E8%B3%BCLP6%E4%B8%80%E6%88%BF?mtc=rwcmd5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fps.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2167958%2F%25E5%2590%2591%25E9%259A%2585%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E7%25B5%2582%25E5%259C%2593%25E7%25BD%25AE%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E5%25A4%25A2%2B%25E9%25BB%2583%25E5%25B0%258F%25E5%25A7%2590%25E5%25A4%25A5%25E5%25BC%259F%25E5%25BC%259F500%25E8%2590%25AC%25E8%25B3%25BCLP6%25E4%25B8%2580%25E6%2588%25BF%3Fmtc%3Drwcmd5&d=K%2BiddrwNjGpv%2BTt7PTNmeZ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=2147e2db\" target=\"_blank\">https://ps.hket.com/article/2167958/%E5%90%91%E9%9A%85%E5%AE%A2%E7%B5%82%E5%9C%93%E7%BD%AE%E6%A5%AD%E5%A4%A2+%E9%BB%83%E5%B0%8F%E5%A7%90%E5%A4%A5%E5%BC%9F%E5%BC%9F500%E8%90%AC%E8%B3%BCLP6%E4%B8%80%E6%88%BF?mtc=rwcmd5</a>"}]}